y won\'t sue us for saying so.\r\n\r\n<div class=\"floatleft\"><iframe src=\"http://rcm.amazon.com/e/cm?t=bitchkittyrac-20&o=1&p=20&l=qs1&f=ifr\" width=\"120\" height=\"90\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></div>\r\n\r\nCDs simply sound the best, and for audiophiles like John nothing else will do.  This is also our DVD store of choice, as they always have the best prices.  Additionally, they stock every entertainment or home need for the brick-and-mortar world.  Amazon is local to Seattle and employs many of our friends and neighbors, making our civic hearts feel good. ANYTHING you want, they have, from music to books to movies to kitchen utensils to magazine subscriptions, etc.  \r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n','59');
