INSERT INTO `page_parts` (`id`,`name`,`filter_id`,`content`,`page_id`) VALUES ('434','body','Textile','*Editorial Guidelines*\r\n\r\nBitch Kitty Racing publishes essays, interviews, photography, informative articles, and lifestyle columns. Our goal is to entertain and inform, in that order. We are striving for intelligent and imaginative conversation about fun topics. We are seeking different viewpoints from around the world.\r\n\r\nArticles and photos should present a clear and simple idea, presented in an entertaining and insightful manner. We want to respect our readers by assuming they are well-read and thoughtful people. We want to challenge them with compelling imagery and genuinely interesting subject matter.\r\n\r\nSubmission Guidelines\r\n\r\n* Bitch Kitty Racing does not accept simultaneous submissions. We prefer to see one submission from an artist or writer at a time.\r\n* We will accept the finished article only. Please send the plain text via email.\r\n* Please submit photos by sending us sample jpegs no more than 470 pixels on the large side, and no more than two at a time.\r\n* We assume North American and foreign publishing rights and an option on republication. All other rights are retained by the writer or artist.\r\n* We do not offer monetary compensation at this time.\r\n\r\n<script src=\"http://www.google-analytics.com/urchin.js\" type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n</script>\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n_uacct = \"UA-1192760-1\";\r\nurchinTracker();\r\n</script>','121');
INSERT INTO `page_parts` (`id`,`name`,`filter_id`,`content`,`page_id`) VALUES ('435','body','Textile','Joanna Newsom\'s second album is a work of genius.  Strings accompany the harpist as she wends her way through much longer pieces, much more intricate than her first offering, more mature.  Her voice, though practice or editing, has mellowed a bit, though the adolescent boy honking is still there, and still charming as hell.\r\n\r\nI have listend to _Ys_ about fifty times and always find something new to love.','122');
