INSERT INTO `page_parts` (`id`,`name`,`filter_id`,`content`,`page_id`) VALUES ('481','body','Textile','Keith and Sabine say I need a vacation.  I personally have no idea what they\'re talking about as I sit here drinking \"mezcal\":http://www.bartonbrands.com/montealbanmezcal.html straight from the bottle.  I\'ve been asked to visit Cancun.\r\n\r\nOn Expedia.com I was asked which \"United States\":http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_States I meant.  Hope that helps Expedia figure it out.  Let me know if you need a flashlight. \r\n\r\nThis is a \"Bitch Kitty submission\":http://bitchkittyracing.com/news/we-need-a-kitty from Chris Nolastname.  I like it.  It looks like a skinny \"Pasha,\":http://bitchkittyracing.com/articles/hammer-and-tongs though I do wonder what the hell the \"thing\" is on the right side.    It\'s obviously drawn on a cocktail napkin, which makes it even drunkenly cooler.\r\n\r\n<txp:upm_image type=\"image\" image_id=\"249\" class=\"image\" />\r\n\r\nKeith\'s and John\'s favorite album of 2006:   <a href=\"http://click.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/stat?id=9Nl7gDS2xmY&offerid=78941&type=3&subid=0&tmpid=1826&RD_PARM1=http%253A%252F%252Fphobos.apple.com%252FWebObjects%252FMZStore.woa%252Fwa%252FviewAlbum%253Fi%253D115581381%2526id%253D115581887%2526s%253D143441%2526partnerId%253D30\">\r\n  <img height=\"15\" width=\"61\" alt=\"We Are Scientists - With Love and Squalor\" src=\"http://ax.phobos.apple.com.edgesuite.net/images/badgeitunes61x15dark.gif\"></img>\r\n</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://click.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/click?id=9Nl7gDS2xmY&offerid=88046.10000019&type=3&subid=0\">Book&nbsp;Now&nbsp;and&nbsp;Save&nbsp;70%&nbsp;on&nbsp;New&nbsp;York&nbsp;Hotels&nbsp;at&nbsp;LastMinuteTravel.com!</a><IMG border=0 width=1 height=1 src=\"http://ad.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/show?id=9Nl7gDS2xmY&bids=88046.10000019&type=3&subid=0\" > ','133');
