INSERT INTO `page_parts` (`id`,`name`,`filter_id`,`content`,`page_id`) VALUES ('484','body','Textile','<a href=\"http://click.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/click?id=9Nl7gDS2xmY&offerid=78941.538627628&type=10&subid=\">Bitch Kitty Records: Punk\r\n</a><img alt=\"icon\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://ad.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/show?id=9Nl7gDS2xmY&bids=78941.538627628&type=10&subid=\">\r\n\r\nI am unreasonably chipper this evening, so I have decided to clear up some restaurant questions.\r\n\r\n#  Yes, the fish and chips is served with fries.\r\n#  A Gin and Tonic is made with gin and a preparation of soda and quinine, a malaria medicine.\r\n#  The cheapest beer is Tray, a lovely blend of whatever happens to be in the beer catch at the moment.\r\n#  Yes, I\'m sorry, the kitchen is closed.  Unfortunately, this does mean there is no more food being cooked.  I\'d be more than happy to root around in the fridge and see what I can get for you, though.  No, I won\'t cook it.  \r\n#  I\'m sorry, the bar is closed.  Yes, that does mean you can have no more alcohol.  No, not even for one hundred dollars.  If you\'d like, I\'d be more than happy to take that hundred and go on a beer run for us, though.\r\n#  My favorite item on the menu?  Oh, it\'s this one right here, the most expensive one.  \r\n#  What\'s our best steak?  Oh, it\'s this one right here, the most expensive one. \r\n#  What\'s my name?  What do you want it to be?  \r\n#  What do I do when I\'m not here?  Oh, I live in a closet and they just turn me on when my shift begins.\r\n#  What else do I do when I\'m not here?  Oh, I just sit around rubbing oil on my bathing suit area.  \r\n\r\nI hope that helps clear up any menu or server questions you all may have. I\'m just going to go oil myself up and think of you.\r\n\r\n<iframe src=\"http://rcm.amazon.com/e/cm?t=bitchkittyrac-20&o=1&p=15&l=st1&mode=books&search=dating&nou=1&fc1=976621&lt1=_blank&lc1=757A6E&bg1=232320&f=ifr\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=\"468\" height=\"240\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:none;\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>','134');
