INSERT INTO `page_parts` (`id`,`name`,`filter_id`,`content`,`page_id`) VALUES ('490','body','Textile','My coworker asked me the other day, \"John, which would you rather: have the best sex of your life that just keeps getting better and better every time, or any car in the world?\"\r\n\r\nShe laughed at me because I couldn\'t answer right away.  Don\'t get me wrong, I love sex.  We\'re like this (holds up two crossed fingers).  But, you see, I\'ve had sex before.  I\'ve never had a \"1961 Aston Martin DB4 GT Zagato.\":http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aston_Martin_DB4_GT_Zagato\r\n\r\nBesides, what is the best sex of your life?  It\'s a difficult question.  I\'d have to say the best sex of my life so far has been when I desire the person most, i.e. when I\'m in love.  Everyone knows that kind of love, when the mere presence of the person in the room sparks a desire for intimacy.  Not sex, particularly, but intimacy.  You\'ve already had sex and are truly, deeply, madly in love with one another.  You want to be as close as possible to your love.  That kind of sex has such a bonding experience woven into it that it\'s positively trancendental.  You want to be wholly inside the other person, like you want to eat her or have her somehow inhabit your skin.  It\'s far more than just intercourse. \r\n\r\nThen there\'s really hot sex, the sex you remember for the rest of your life.  It may have been a one-off, it may have been a passing lover, it may have been a girlfriend.  It\'s the sex you think about during masturbation.  Sometimes it\'s the sex you\'ll never share with another because you wouldn\'t know how to ask someone to do that, at least not if you don\'t want her to think you\'re a \"completely perverted freak.\":http://bitchkittyracing.com/articles/strange-brunette-in-my-bed \r\n\r\nSometimes a person enters your life and you can\'t think of anything else but having sex with her.  You can\'t be around her without acting like an idiot.  Sometimes it\'s love, but most often it\'s lust.  You know damned well a relationship is impossible, but you\'re at least going to see her naked.  This can be the hottest one-night stand on the planet, or it can be a relationship that drags on way too long because the sex is so phenomenal. It\'s different than really hot sex because it\'s a direct product of the person you\'re with rather than what you did with that person. \r\n\r\nWhat other kinds of sex are there?  I\'m sure there are several thousands.  For me, though, I\'m going say the best sex is really hot sex with someone you can\'t resist with whom you happen to be madly in love.  Would I trade that for my Aston Martin? \r\n\r\nDon\'t ask me that question.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://click.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/click?id=9Nl7gDS2xmY&offerid=78941.538307636&type=10&subid=\">Bitch Kitty Records: Transgenerational Dating, a mix tape to show your younger lover that you still rock\r\n</a><img alt=\"icon\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://ad.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/show?id=9Nl7gDS2xmY&bids=78941.538307636&type=10&subid=\">','136');
