INSERT INTO `page_parts` (`id`,`name`,`filter_id`,`content`,`page_id`) VALUES ('697','body','Textile','I had a party of four come in to the restaurant last night, tourists from Germany.  It was past last call, but as one member of the party was a breathtakingly beautiful Teutonic Valkyrie who asked, \"May ve haff a taple?\" I took their orders anyway, my brain flooding with images of her in a skin tight, leather-skirted SS uniform, complete with jack boots and  a riding crop, shining golden hair pulled tightly back under her _Feldmutze,_ finding ways to make me talk... \r\n\r\nI was rapidly losing the ability to think as I checked her ID to make sure she was old enough to drink here in the States.  Her name was Heike, Heike from Hamburg. My imagination took over...\r\n\r\nbq. _A dark dusty basement in Hamburg, 1944, a single dim bulb lighting only the center of the room, two simple and war-scarred chairs on either side of an ugly but stout table, the sounds of a tank battle raging in the city overhead_\r\n\r\nbq. \"But, Heike!  You love me!\"  I can\'t escape.\r\n \r\nbq. \"Ich liebe dich doch.\"  A single tear escapes her eye, an eye the color of the Cotes d\'Provence, where we first fell in love, before the war.  \"Aber das machts jetzt nichts.  Ich muss...\" And so she begins to do what she must for the Fatherland.\r\n\r\nBack in reality\r\n\r\n\r\n','206');
