INSERT INTO `page_parts` (`id`,`name`,`filter_id`,`content`,`page_id`) VALUES ('721','body','Markdown','Bitch Kitty Racing has two great new articles on internet dating by Rebecca Dallin, [Profile Writing for Men](http://bitchkittyracing.com/articles/internet-dating-writing-for-men/) and [The Game Show](http://bitchkittyracing.com/articles/internet-dating-the-game-show/).\r\n\r\nWe have been handily thumping away at the back end for the last couple weeks, making upgrades and preparing to roll out a few new features.  As many of you have noticed, BKR uses a Ruby powered [Radiant CMS](http://radiantcms.org/).  Radiant is currently on version <del>0.5</del> 0.6 and Keith is one of those fighting the good fight and bringing Radiant up to 1.0.  Sometimes we want features which simply aren\'t available yet, and Keith is one of those who makes them.\r\n\r\n<em>Dear non-tech people,</em>\r\n\r\n<em>Thanks for staying with us through that.  John fell asleep at the words <br/> \"back end,\" so you\'re doing well.</em>\r\n\r\nEpisode 8 of Bitch Kitty Racing TV will be released this week!  If you\'d like, you can [subscribe to BKRTV](http://phobos.apple.com/WebObjects/MZStore.woa/wa/viewPodcast?id=218845173&s=143441) at iTunes.  That way you\'ll have it the moment it becomes available.  The new show promises to be utterly bizarre. No teasers!\r\n\r\nBITCH KITTY RACING WOULD LIKE TO HEAR FROM YOU!\r\n\r\nWe had a lot of fun with your submissions last week and thought, y\'know, maybe you\'d like to do it again sometime.  Like NOW!\r\n\r\nWe\'re making another [iMix](http://bitchkittyracing.com/bitch-kitty-records/imixes/) and would like to know, *What\'s the Most Embarrassing Song on Your iPod?*\r\n\r\nHere, we\'ll start:\r\n\r\n>\"Diamonds are a Girl\'s Best Friend\" by Marilyn Monroe <cite>John P, Writer, 28</cite>\r\n\r\n>\"I Touch Myself\" by The Divinyls <cite>Frank, Attorney, 39</cite>\r\n\r\n>\"Friends in Low Places\" by Garth Brooks<cite>Inge, Restaurant Manager, 31</cite>\r\n\r\nYou get the idea. Please send them to: <submissions@bitchkittyracing.com>.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n','216');
