INSERT INTO `page_parts` (`id`,`name`,`filter_id`,`content`,`page_id`) VALUES ('786','body','Textile','On my recent visit to Seattle to have a first face to face meeting of the BKR Triumvirate (I have known John my entire adult life, but Kevin is new to me), John expressed interest in a new Blog section for himself. As long as I was at it, I thought I would program one for myself. So check out \"http://keith.bitchkittyracing.com\":http://keith.bitchkittyracing.com for new photos and whatever else I feel like putting up. And look at -out- for \"http://john.bitchkittyracing.com\":john.bitchkittyracing.com, its -not- ready, -but soon will be-.\r\n\r\nNow, writing is not my thing. While I actually enjoy it, the duties of squashing bugs, making things work, and taking the occasional picture mean that my time for writing is limited to train rides. Thankfully, most German trains have power these days. \r\n\r\nIn any case, because it is relatively hard to make myself write and I have _so_ many pictures, I decided to make it something of a photo blog. BKR\'s \"galleries\":http://bitchkittyracing.com/galleries have been down for months (I had to write a fully new gallery system) so maybe this will go a ways to filling them back up. \r\n\r\nJohn has recorded my entire sleepless, drunken trip to Seattle in excruciating detail, which will be online shortly. These are a few shots from that and whatever else I have been up to lately. Look for regular updates. \r\n\r\nAnd as soon as John recovers from his birthday, he will have some new bloggy stuff too. It will only get better.','245');
