INSERT INTO `page_parts` (`id`,`name`,`filter_id`,`content`,`page_id`) VALUES ('804','body','Markdown','Holy crap!  Not much time left to prepare for the highlights of Summer, the best of the best, the brightest points in the car geek\'s life: The Monaco Grand Prix, The 24 Hours of Le Mans, and The Puget Sound All British Field Meet.\r\n\r\n**May 27**, [Monaco Grand Prix](http://www.formula1.com/race/circuitmap/774.html)\r\n\r\n> This is the yearly return of Christ for both F1 and vintage racing fans alike.  While I would be happy to argue the sanctity of any circuit, Monaco walks on water.  The rich history, the romantic and ultra-hip setting and, let\'s face it, the tunnel.  \r\nOh God, oh God...  Was it good for you, dear?\r\n\r\n**June 16-17**, [24 Heures du Mans](http://www.lemans.org/24heuresdumans/live/pages/accueil_gb.html)\r\n\r\n> ProDrive now owns Aston Martin, and I have no doubt they have something to prove.  Watch the greatest and best of all endurance road races, and if you have the ability, please get me a damned ticket!  I have no intention of sleeping for a moment of this most historic and hallowed of races.  Oh, and Audi will undoubtedly be there, too, with their diesel race car.  Um, hey Audi, uh, perhaps you could switch to a GT class and let somebody else win LMP for once.  Have you ever hear of the English word \"gloating?\"\r\n\r\n**July 28**, [All British Field Meet](http://www.abfm.com/abfm.htm)  \r\nBellevue Community College, Washington, US  \r\n\r\n>\"Do you know why the English drink warm beer?  Lucas manufactures their refrigerators.\"  \r\n\r\n>\"Did you know that Lucas made a vacuum cleaner? It was the only product they made that didn\'t suck.\"  \r\n\r\n>\"Lucas light switch settings: dim, flicker, and burn.\"  \r\n\r\nCome one, come all, my stubborn and backwards brothers and sisters!  Let us pay Ohmage to the Prince of Darkness!  \r\n','250');
