INSERT INTO `page_parts` (`id`,`name`,`filter_id`,`content`,`page_id`) VALUES ('841','body','Textile','<r:asset name=\"TITLE.JPG\">\r\n<r:link size=\"display\" rel=\"lightbox\"><r:image size=\"thumbnail\" /></r:link>\r\n</r:asset>\r\n\r\nAs you might know from Viewer Mail, Too, I did a short for the local porn festival (obviously this is John).  It\'s called Zombie Tapioca Lovefest 4000 and will be shown over October 5 and 6 at On the Boards, here in Seattle, under the aegis of The Stranger\'s third annual Hump amateur porn festival.  ZTL 4000 will not be posted on Bitch Kitty Racing; I do not consider it appropriate for all-ages public consumption.\r\n\r\nWe had a screening of ZTL at our local private club and invited everyone we could think of.  It was a resounding success and there were two unrelated producers in the audience.  This is where it gets funny: The sequel to ZTL 4000 will be a short film. I am also doing an unrelated television pilot as the host of a science (science-type) show.  \r\n\r\n<r:asset name=\"Zombie_Fight.png\">\r\n<r:link size=\"display\" rel=\"lightbox\"><r:image size=\"thumbnail\" /></r:link>\r\n</r:asset>\r\n\r\nMy head got huge for a few weeks there and I was an insufferable, egotistical ass.  Even more so than normal.  My feet are back on the ground now and I apologize to anyone who may have been bumped by my bloated sense of false self-importance.  (As an aside, Keith I played in a band called The Shit Kittens.  Our hit single was called John\'s Ego.)  Having a movie in pre-production does not make one an award-winning, avant-garde director.  Doing a pilot for a show does not give one a successful series.  I am extremely thankful to have been asked to do these projects, and am trying to keep my eyes wide open during the experience--I don\'t want to miss a minute of it.  \r\n\r\nZombie Tapioca Lovefest 4000 will be shown publicly, however.  The time and dates will be posted here and everywhere else I can think of.  Wish the BKR team good luck at Hump.  A win there means a lot in terms of publicity, a lot in terms of bragging rights, and a lot in the increased ability to raise money for UNDEAD GIRLS.  You want to see this film.  Release date: 8/8/2008.\r\n\r\nPure rot and roll!','271');
INSERT INTO `page_parts` (`id`,`name`,`filter_id`,`content`,`page_id`) VALUES ('844','body','Textile','h2. <r:title />\r\n\r\n\"A POP ROCK ZOMBIE ARMAGEDDON LOVE STORY\"\r\n\r\n!http://casketgirlsthemovie.com/assets/413/Casket_Girls_Placeholder.jpg!\r\n\r\nCASKET GIRLS is an independent movie that is fully owned by John Moroney and Loren Weisman. No percentages or debts were accrued in the making of this film.  One half of all proceeds from all sales of Casket Girls goes to \"Northwest Harvest\":http://www.northwestharvest.org and their \"Three Squares for Kids\":http://www.northwestharvest.org/threesquares.html program, providing nourishment for children who go hungry when school is not in session.\r\n\r\np=. BKR & PM ENTERTAINMENT PRESENT <br/>\r\nJOHN MORONEY  JENNIFER DANTES in \"CASKET GIRLS\" <br/>\r\nwith KIMBERLY GARDINA  CRISTINA KNUTSON  JEFF WILLEY <br/>  \r\nproduced by LOREN WEISMAN <br/>\r\nwritten and directed by JOHN MORONEY <br/>\r\na BOTTOM OF THE FIFTH PRODUCTION  \r\n\r\n','273');
INSERT INTO `page_parts` (`id`,`name`,`filter_id`,`content`,`page_id`) VALUES ('846','body','Textile','h2. <r:title />\r\n\r\nCASKET GIRLS is an independent movie that is fully owned by John Moroney and Loren Weisman. No percentages or debts were accrued in the making of this film.  One half of all proceeds from all sales of Casket Girls goes to \"Northwest Harvest\":http://www.northwestharvest.org and their \"Three Squares for Kids\":http://www.northwestharvest.org/threesquares.html program, providing nourishment for children who go hungry when school is not in session.\r\n\r\n\r\np=. BKR & PM ENTERTAINMENT PRESENT\r\nJOHN MORONEY  JENNIFER DANTES in \"CASKET GIRLS\"  \r\nwith JEFF WILLEY  CRISTINA KNUTSON  KIMBERLY GARDENA\r\nstory by JOHN MORONEY and LOREN WEISMAN\r\nmusic by LOREN WEISMAN AND SCOTT ROSS\r\nproduced by LOREN WEISMAN  directed by JOHN MORONEY\r\nA MORONEY & WEISMAN PRODUCTION','274');
INSERT INTO `page_parts` (`id`,`name`,`filter_id`,`content`,`page_id`) VALUES ('847','body','Textile','<r:asset name=\"Scan20001.jpg\">\r\n<r:link size=\"display\" rel=\"lightbox\"><r:image size=\"thumbnail\" /></r:link>\r\n</r:asset>\r\n\r\nWell, the Hump! fest begins tonight.  The local rag that is sponsoring the event provided an encapsulation of the twenty films selected.  All were synopses and previews, except for one entry: ours.  I can\'t help but feel a little proud.  This is the second time we\'ve been mentioned in the paper, and the short hasn\'t even been screened yet! \r\n\r\n<r:asset name=\"Hump_Ad_2.jpg\">\r\n<r:link size=\"display\" rel=\"lightbox\"><r:image size=\"thumbnail\" /></r:link>\r\n</r:asset>  Here\'s the first one.\r\n\r\nOh, and \"CASKET GIRLS\":http://casketgirls.net is steaming along nicely!  The site is up, and now I need to design it so you can see what we\'re about!\r\n\r\nThanks, everybody.  It\'s been a really great year!  Wish us luck tonight and tomorrow at HUMP!\r\n\r\nCASKET GIRLS\r\n\"A pop rock zombie armageddon love story.\"  ','275');
INSERT INTO `page_parts` (`id`,`name`,`filter_id`,`content`,`page_id`) VALUES ('848','body','Textile','From the Stranger\'s blog, October 8, 2007\r\n\r\n\"Zombie Tapioca Lovefest 4000, with 423 votes. \r\n\r\nAfter sleeping with every freak in Seattle, a desperate mana cute desperate mandecides to go for the only thrill left: fucking the dead. Well, the undead. In a tub full of tapioca pudding. Great production values, hilarious dialogue, and a cunnilingus scene that will live in infamy. Truly outstanding.\"','276');
