INSERT INTO `page_parts` (`id`,`name`,`filter_id`,`content`,`page_id`) VALUES ('896','body','Textile','Ghosts and ghouls and goblins, oh my!\r\n\r\nHappy Halloween from Keith, Kevin, myself, and the entire Bitch Kitty Racing team!  We\'re celebrating our second birthday.  Thank you all, and my special thanks to Keith for making Bitch Kitty Racing a reality!  \r\n\r\nBOO!  I dressed up in four different outfits this year.  Our Halloween special shows one.  Here\'s another: I was a guy who ran wrong with the Mob and was buried in the New Jersey Pine Barrens for a month after being murdered.  Tonight I\'ll be a guy who is being eaten alive by spiders.  Friday I was Vampire Kuddelz.  Thursday I was Zombie Kuddelz.\r\n\r\nI love Halloween!\r\n\r\nJohn Moroney <br/>\r\nSeattle\r\n\r\n\r\n!http://bitchkittyracing.com/assets/417/jenny10.jpg!\r\n','298');
INSERT INTO `page_parts` (`id`,`name`,`filter_id`,`content`,`page_id`) VALUES ('897','body','Textile','Part of the preparation for my role in Casket Girls is physical.  Actually, most of it is, as I\'m basically playing myself.  I\'m not an actor; I\'m a pretender.  That does not get me off the hook for having any fight sequences look realistic enough to pass, however.  To that end I\'m searching for a flashy martial arts instructor for not just myself, but the core cast and everyone else who\'s interested.  <br><br>I\'ve also asked a friend to be my personal trainer.  We\'re doing a lot of strength training right now, and the combination of heavy lifting and a low fat/high protein diet has a rather bizarre side effect: I\'m craving blood.  <br><br>Really.  I want to attack a large animal and drink it dry.  Even human beings are starting to look tasty.  I\'ve started supplementing my diet with beef, but even cold rare it\'s not bloody enough.  I think they wash it out.  I\'ve started taking a multivitamin with iron in it.  Hopefully, whatever it is I\'m craving is in there somewhere.<br><br>Maybe I\'ll just split food with the cat.<br><br>John Moroney<br>Seattle','299');
INSERT INTO `page_parts` (`id`,`name`,`filter_id`,`content`,`page_id`) VALUES ('898','body','Textile','Hey, all!\r\n\r\nThis Christmas, rather than buying your coworker a $5 gift certificate for one cup of coffee, why not give that same coworker the warm fuzzy feeling that comes with not letting a small child die of malnutrition?  \r\n\r\nFind the local food network in your area and donate the $5 to them.  Please.  Your coworker has food, shelter, and clothing.  There are far too many that don\'t even have that.  \r\n\r\nHere is a handy link to the organization in Washington State: \r\n\r\n<a href = \"http://www.northwestharvest.org/\">Northwest Harvest</a>\r\n\r\nIf you are reading this on a computer, I\'d like t remind you that many people don\'t even have electricity.  Please count your blessings this season and share.  Every tiny bit helps.','300');
